{"title":"Canyon Neuron CF gives versatile 130mm trail bike travel boost, geometry tweak for bigger adventure","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/04/canyon-neuron-cf-gives-versatile-130mm-trail-bike-travel-boost-geometry-tweak-for-bigger-adventure/","date":1636030849000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"625\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails-800x625.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails-800x625.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails-297x232.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails-120x94.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails-768x600.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails-1536x1200.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091625/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_trails.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-277374\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Canyon’s carbon Neuron CF all-rounder trail bike adds an extra 10mm of fork travel for 2022, boosting its technical trail capabilities while retaining pedaling efficiency. The new 130/140mm travel setup situates the updated Neuron in a nice middle ground –&nbsp;equally fun to rail smooth singletrack, smash around on technical trails,&nbsp;and still capable to head out for all-day backcountry adventure rides. You know, just a mountain bike.</p><h2>2022 Canyon Neuron CF 130/140mm trail mountain bike</h2><div id=\"attachment_277416\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277416\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, complete\" width=\"1650\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete.jpg 1650w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete-297x180.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete-800x485.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete-120x73.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete-768x465.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091620/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_complete-1536x931.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1650px) 100vw, 1650px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277416\">c. Canyon</p></div><p>As much as mountain bikes become ever more specialized, longer travel, and slacker… there’s a lot to be said for that versatile sweet-spot mid-travel trail bike that could be a perfect fit for most rides and riders. That’s always been where the Neuron sat. And now with a bit more travel up front, it slots even more nicely in between Canyon’s longer XC-focused <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=canyon+lux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Lux</a> – now <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/19/review-canyons-longer-lux-trail-bike-proves-a-little-more-suspension-goes-a-long-way/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Trail</em></a> too – and all-mountain <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=canyon+spectral\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Spectral</a> – bleeding into <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/27/review-canyon-spectral-mullet-cf-cllctv-shifts-capable-trail-bike-to-enduro/\"><em>Mullet</em></a> enduro now, as well.</p><h3>Tweaked geometry?</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, trail riding\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding-297x186.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding-800x500.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding-120x75.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091615/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_all-mountain-riding-1536x960.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Following the same successful upgrade on a single premium ultra-limited edition this season, all the new carbon bikes now pair 140mm forks to the same 130mm travel Neuron frames. That bit of extra travel up front slackens the ride out by about 0.5° from the Neuron’s original debut, opening up even steeper trails,&nbsp; now offering 66.5° or 67° head angles (27.5 or 29″, respectively).</p><div id=\"attachment_277414\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277414\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, updated geometry\" width=\"1800\" height=\"975\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry-297x161.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry-800x433.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry-120x65.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry-768x416.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091612/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_updated-geometry-1536x832.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277414\">tweaked 2022 Canyon Neuron CF geometry</p></div><p>Of note, it looks like Canyon has made some other frame geometry tweak somewhere. Because even with the longer fork travel and slacker head angle, frame Stack &amp; Reach is unchanged, the 74.5° seat angle is unchanged, as are the 18 or 38mm BB drop of the original Neuron. (Of note: all of those changed in the 130/140mm CF LTD build of model year 2021.)</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, frame detail\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end.jpg 1400w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end-297x212.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end-800x571.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end-120x86.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091609/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_front-end-768x549.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"></a></p><p>The full-carbon Neuron CF hasn’t really changed at all <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/11/27/canyon-neuron-cf-connects-with-more-riders-for-xc-trail-riding-fun/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">since its late 2018 launch</a>. The 130mm rear is the same supple early travel, efficient pedaling mid-stroke &amp; progressive end-of-travel Triple Phase four-bar suspension.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, suspension detail\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091605/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_rear-end-suspension-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>The bikes use size specific wheels, so 27.5 for XS &amp; S and 29″ for M-XL.</p><div id=\"attachment_277411\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277411\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, 27.5 or 29er\" width=\"2519\" height=\"1417\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork.jpg 2519w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091600/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_275-wheel-in-29er-fork-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2519px) 100vw, 2519px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277411\">27.5″ wheels in 29″ forks</p></div><p>Interestingly, even the smaller 27.5″ wheeled bikes feature 29er forks. (<em>Read about why <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/11/27/canyon-neuron-cf-connects-with-more-riders-for-xc-trail-riding-fun/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</em>) So I wonder how many riders might have already tried to convert their bikes to mullets to get a similar performance boost like this longer fork travel offers?)</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, details\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details-297x165.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details-800x444.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details-768x427.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091556/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_frame-details-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p>The Neuron also features internal/external cable management through a full-length downtube protector, a threaded BB, a headset steering stop to prevent crash damage, 30.9 dropper posts, and is 1x/2x compatible even if all bike builds stick with a single chainring</p><h3>2022 Canyon Neuron CF – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3><div id=\"attachment_277409\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091553/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike