Canyon Neuron CF 8</p></div><p>Four carbon Neuron CF models are available now with the entry 3000€ 2022 Canyon Neuron CF 8 &amp; CF 8 WMN shipping as of today with a Shimano SLX 1×12 drivetrain, FOX 34 &amp; Float DPS Performance suspension, a Canyon Iridium dropper, and DT Swiss XM 1700 alloy wheels (13.3-13.5kg).</p><div id=\"attachment_277407\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277407\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel,CF\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091545/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277407\">2022 Canyon Neuron CF 9</p></div><p>The 4000€ Neuron CF 9 upgrades to Shimano XT and Fox Performance Elite suspension, shipping soon to later this winter depending on sizing.</p><div id=\"attachment_277406\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277406\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel,CF 9 SL\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091541/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-9-sl-complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277406\">2022 Canyon Neuron CF 9 SL</p></div><p>Then, a $6500 / 4800€ Neuron CF 9 SL shifts to a wireless SRAM GX Eagle AXS drivetrain, Code RSC brakes, Fox Factory suspension, and carbon DT XMC 1501 wheels at a claimed weight of 12.96kg (M), expected in the second half of December.</p><div id=\"attachment_277405\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091538/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-slx-ltd-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277405\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091538/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-slx-ltd-complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Canyon Neuron CF carbon trail mountain bike, updated 130mm rear, longer 140mm fork travel, CF SLX LTD\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091538/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-slx-ltd-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091538/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_neuron-cf-slx-ltd-complete-2