ontent/uploads/2021/11/04091534/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_MTB-group-ride.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091534/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_MTB-group-ride-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091534/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_MTB-group-ride-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091534/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_MTB-group-ride-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091534/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_MTB-group-ride-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04091534/2022-Canyon-Neuron-CF-carbon-trail-mountain-bike_updated-130mm-rear_new-longer-140mm-fork-travel_MTB-group-ride-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>US availability of any of the updated Neurons still seems up in the air. Only the CF 9 SL is currently listed by Canyon USA, with availability times quoted either as “Spring 2022” or (yikes!) “Fall 2023” depending on size…</p><p><a href=\"https://www.canyon.com/\"><em>Canyon.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"000ed0a6608f6648aa54aac7171e0e185b584e5679b7237806129342098c739c","category":"Cycling"}